name: Token of Gratitude GENESIS black
description: Token of Gratitude GENESIS black - first NFT of our global charitable initiative. Token of Gratitude - a first in the world charitable initiative that utilizes organic musical inspiration and harnesses the power of Creative AI (Musical Blockchain) and NFT technology to give back. It is the showcase of the next level of machine-human creative collaboration. Proceeds from sales will be distributed among the partner funds to help music people behind the scenes in the music industry. More information, news and other exclusives: https://tog.foundation/
